Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走開，妳擋不住的!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這片朗朗晴空裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的心情 飛散灑滿其中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.21,0:00:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果命中註定的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠是你那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現實卻無法如願以償
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:01:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在閃耀光芒的風裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.39,0:01:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想的羽毛 飄然飛揚落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.83,0:01:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣邁向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.54,0:01:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就這麼美麗地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始奔騰的熱烈心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.68,0:01:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躍動出跟那一天同樣的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你率直的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能永遠看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第3話 炎之舞／星之誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不會燙？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣，妳冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫做武具
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是HiME力量的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真讓人驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就第一次而言\N她表現得算是很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌勒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣也是HiME對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:03:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是搞錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔～它就叫做搞錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把劍叫做彌勒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過別牽扯得太深入嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位，要開打還太早了點唷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝填鉻彈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真耐打
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答應過媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣，看看後面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接了當的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子一直在這裡守護著妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦具土
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到\N這孩子竟然是妳的心之子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識牠…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，心之子是HiME的守護神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，抉擇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是否要接納那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要跟迦具土一同作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣\N不，舞衣公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別聽他說得天花亂墜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我不用再強調了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要戰鬥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就非得賭上妳最重視的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說要賭上我的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就賭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是舞衣公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔起封印之劍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦具土
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦具土？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦具土，你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命!玖我同學!快逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊…姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣好強喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點啊\N舞衣!舞衣!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣，巧海就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸也穩定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，昨晚的狀況\N確實是有點危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊…姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草皮燒完後換燒後山嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是不缺話題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縱火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能燒成那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是幽浮著地的痕跡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太扯了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執行部長珠洲城好像氣炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵著說要組成調查委員會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰介紹個男人給她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，哪來的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我的藝術品整個泡湯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查出來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:12:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是獲得了\N風花獎學金才來這裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼在意她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟後山的事情有關連？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想把靜留牽扯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳嘴巴真甜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎學長，再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家路上小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，學長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果創立祭該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為發生了那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想在船上辦宴會的企畫\N大概是不可行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得從頭重新來過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我短時間內也不想再搭船了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次會派你\N到安全一點的地方去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不算方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖我夏姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，打擾二位了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個冒失鬼，氣氛正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的，別急嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，幫妳泡杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是有不錯的曼特寧嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是要我泡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳可以好好休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是學生會室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要\N勉強自己到會發病的程度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是\N跟昨晚的事情有關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃，這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我不太記得昨晚的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？不記得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，在這裡在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是受理事長所託
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來接鴇羽同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說有事要跟妳講\N要我們來叫妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了，後山的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校方歸納出正式看法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是落雷造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你偷聽到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是老樣子，扮豬吃老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不懂是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是過獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過\N能不能放過巧海同學一馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在非常需要休養
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶他回宿舍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯，你陪一下舞衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副會長好像很不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種細心大哥哥的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在各方面都算是個厲害角色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和藤乃會長一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為校史上最強一對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，已經死會了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打雷會弄到這種地步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡輪的事情也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的災害真的層出不窮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是被什麼給附身了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看見了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣，要不要去收個驚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我介紹妳便宜的地方如何？\N我是說真的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來\N你不是不想跟我有所牽扯了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也不用突然對我生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉唆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們等妳很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽舞衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是那時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳們兩位已經是好朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是風華學園理事長\N風花真白小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到風華學園\N鴇羽舞衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼～？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 原來父母都已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身體又不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是給姊姊添了很多麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，能夠申請到獎學金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊唸書，我真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊之前\N我跟姊姊兩個人約定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好享受校園生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是個好姊姊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事長小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳批准我的獎學金申請案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想\N到學校之後要來拜會妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻遇到很多事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不用對我道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是有目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才讓妳到這間學校來就讀的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓身為HiME的各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚妳們對抗的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個被稱作無依者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無依者…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是從這個世界\N而是從某處迷途而出的異形
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠打倒牠們的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有受到星星引導的少女之力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們HiME而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才將我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓我們跟那些怪物戰鬥\N才找我們過來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種作法真的太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有非做不可的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我既沒有餘力\N也沒有空去管其他事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要照顧弟弟…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳不介意的話，由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，是我失言了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了的是妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就弄東西給妳吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著，眼睛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦\N我不是叫妳眼睛閉起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是，竟然連放熱水都不會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底住在多鄉下的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想拒絕的話，我不會強迫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.99,0:19:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣我也不會收回獎學金
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做，還請妳們自己決定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說命啊，妳打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要照那個理事長說的\N投身戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上她算是妳的監護人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的生活費和學費\N都是她在打理的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找出兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有敵人妨礙，我就戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是既來之則安之吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺說過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長在封架之地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣跟我在一起會覺得麻煩？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有別的地方可去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀討厭，命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，妳真是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前一片花～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，抓緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像中的還適合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來，這給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便當，這是妳的份
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？舞衣的室友？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫…美袋命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國中部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.77,0:21:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾年級？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14歲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是3年級
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧!好可愛～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.86,0:22:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請別迷惘」\N這句話我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有無法傳達給你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過寂寞的笑容搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫過傷口 Lonely good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連熱情都會讓我痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋著永恆的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是我的天空我的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那段燃燒熔化的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.67,0:23:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記 請你好好記著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要收藏在心底就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Search for my life\N總有一天還會再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是喜歡你那清澈的雙眼\N現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.19,0:23:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走上各自的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新開始前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風的惡 ． 作 ． 劇\N喂…玖我同學\N妳那樣子坐會被看光喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.75,0:23:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.72,0:23:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為事實就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.39,0:23:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.35,0:23:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果太依賴這點\N遲早會吃大虧的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.42,0:23:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思\N做得到的話就來試試看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.66,0:23:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安，我是瀨能葵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.76,0:24:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨～我是原田千繪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.90,0:24:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天來為各位介紹我們班
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.53,0:24:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風華學園高中部1年A班
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.77,0:24:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是班上所有同學
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.17,0:24:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都有名字耶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.61,0:24:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千繪，妳在說什麼啊\N這不是理所當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.98,0:24:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這個，今天有一名轉學生\N將要來到我們1-A了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.35,0:24:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第一天上課下午就突然蹺課
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.99,0:24:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.36,0:24:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許她現在\N正遭遇很不得了的狀況？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.63,0:24:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說\N是讓人很有興趣的人才吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.43,0:24:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就打入\N風華學園大奶排行榜內
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.77,0:24:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這種排行榜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.80,0:24:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.20,0:24:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這一輩子是絲毫\N完全根本不會有任何關連的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.71,0:24:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過份～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.51,0:24:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我再加把勁的話…嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.38,0:24:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（拜託，請把電燈關掉）\N（瀨能葵）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.88,0:24:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.82,0:24:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也拿出珍藏的一張相片!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.96,0:25:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（請忘了昨晚的事 。 ）\N（原田千繪）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.03,0:25:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.83,0:25:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有一天\N能在本篇看到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.23,0:25:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.33,0:25:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好～那麼各位，下回見啦\N（本影像乃是虛構的 。 ）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.10,0:25:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掰～\N（失望了吧。 ）
